Analyze: Identify the learning problem, audience needs, existing knowledge,

00:00:53.950 --> 00:00:54.607
and goals.

00:00:54.750 --> 00:00:59.305
This initial phase involves identifying the learning needs, goals, and constraints.

00:00:59.455 --> 00:01:03.617
Instructional designers assess the target audience's existing knowledge and skills to ensure

00:01:03.767 --> 00:01:07.697
that the training aligns with their needs. Key questions addressed include what learners

00:01:07.847 --> 00:01:10.718
need to know and the context in which the instruction will occur.

