00:01:24.583 --> 00:01:29.295
First D in ADDIE is Design
Plan learning objectives, content structure, assessments,

00:01:29.445 --> 00:01:30.546
and delivery methods.

00:01:30.683 --> 00:01:34.733
In this phase, designers outline the learning objectives and create a detailed plan for the

00:01:34.883 --> 00:01:39.425
instructional materials. This includes selecting appropriate instructional strategies,

00:01:39.575 --> 00:01:43.803
determining the content structure, and designing assessments to measure learning outcomes.

00:01:45.750 --> 00:01:49.934
Develop
Second D in ADDIE is Develop
Create and assemble

00:01:50.084 --> 00:01:54.142
course materials, including media, activities, and prototypes.

00:01:54.517 --> 00:01:58.542
