Yes, we do.
During development, the actual instructional materials

00:02:11.849 --> 00:02:15.891
are created based on the design plan. This may involve writing content,

00:02:16.041 --> 00:02:20.221
creating multimedia elements, and assembling the course materials. Testing

00:02:20.371 --> 00:02:22.893
