00:02:36.850 --> 00:02:40.784
Evaluate
Finally the E is Evaluate
Assess the

00:02:40.934 --> 00:02:44.972
effectiveness of the training through both formative (ongoing) and summative (

00:02:45.122 --> 00:02:49.452
final) evaluations.
The final phase consists of both formative

00:02:49.602 --> 00:02:53.994
and summative evaluations. Formative evaluation occurs throughout the ADDIE process

00:02:54.144 --> 00:02:58.469
to gather feedback and make improvements, while summative evaluation assesses the effectiveness

00:02:58.619 --> 00:03:02.599
