00:03:37.250 --> 00:03:41.204
ADDIE model 
In short is a systematic instructional design framework

00:03:41.354 --> 00:03:46.034
used to create effective learning experiences. It stands for Analyze, Design,

00:03:46.184 --> 00:03:50.864
Develop, Implement, and Evaluate, each representing a phase in the process.

00:03:51.014 --> 00:03:55.027
The model is a flexible, adaptable, and iterative approach to developing training

00:03:55.177 --> 00:03:59.432
programs and learning materials. 
